[30;1m1729 | [0m[35m        Smith-Waterman or other algorithms, which may not require[0m
[30;1m1730 | [0m[35m        alignments that begin at the first residue or end at the last.[0m
[30;1m1731 | [0m[35m        In addition, extra sequencing adapters, multiplex identifiers,[0m
[30;1m1732 | [0m[35m        and low-quality bases that were not considered for alignment[0m
[30;1m1733 | [0m[35m        may have been retained.[0m
